{"tid":1506210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[不分化不割蓆][經濟就是春袋]下一步點做，去唔去機場?","createTime":"2019-08-25T17:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T23:06:33.000Z","uid":272165,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"fd6a21f6de6effd315f741f9db72e5ab2a3f5dc8","tid":1506210,"uid":272165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:42:15.000Z","msg":"我知連登而家好多鬼，但希望大家唔好因為我係P牌就唔睇，睇完覺得唔啱先再負皮我都未遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小妹由69開始都不停發夢，自問雖然唔係最前線，但都好努力係唔同方面幫手。<br />\n今日係荃灣發夢嗰陣，我好認真咁諗到底仲可以做啲咩，以下係我嘅睇法:<br />\n大家都知黑警港共無法無天惡撚曬，我地要令佢跪低，或者至少局9佢回應我地，一定係要搞9香港經濟。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁點先搞9到經濟? </span></span>我覺得keep住遊行係好撚重要，每個禮拜六日咁抗爭(好撚攰但大家撐住!!!)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />行得多可能會灰心覺得冇撚用，但起碼我地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">令嗰區嘅經濟受影響</span></span>，可能影響到嘅只係小店大家覺得冇撚用，但其實唔係，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">原理就同罷買byebuy一樣</span></span>，短期係未必會見到成果，但只要堅持，無論成效言低都一定會有影響。<br />\n加上係香港其實每區都一定有大商場，今日荃灣SHK嘅荃灣廣場都收咗皮。所以一定要繼續!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後我又諗，每次行完同黑警對峙，到底帶嚟咩?<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">(利申唔係要否定勇武，冇勇武香港已完)</span></span>，但正正因為勇武咁重要而又對我地咁珍貴，相信冇一位手足會希望再有任何同路人被捕同比黑警虐待，而有幾個十幾個甚至更多手被捕就好似係定律咁。<br />\n在此我想指出嘅係，我認為我地做嘅所有嘢都應該係有目的。同黑警對峙目前損己又不利己，因為我地係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">用好多手足換嚟嘅，都唔知有冇一個黑警受傷</span></span>(所以支持有機會嗰陣將狗往死裏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，係唔抵。就好似塞鐵咁，成本高，效益低，咁咪停一停諗一諗。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">敵人反的，我地就要做。</span></span><br />\n垃圾張華峰話要限制我地按錢，我地就要盡力繼續按，而咁樣亦證明<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">任何影響到經濟嘅嘢都係港共至撚驚嘅</span></span>!!!!!!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以我地明知<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">機場係春袋，係唔撚可以放過呀</span></span>!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣唔係要放棄地區，但機場或者係一個相對冇咁損兵折將而又有成效嘅地方!!<br />\n可能又會比人屌係機場撚，但我真心只係想講下我嘅意見，啱就spread開佢同做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申無論機場定地區都會繼續出!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d5dd5a14e732d7bac949a0b29d0844b718c008","tid":1506210,"uid":272165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:42:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1504638/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1504638/page/1</a><br />\n大家可以睇睇呢個PO"},{"pid":"b5b8d72251c24d105da32fc9e8d8dd8a16c8dd3b","tid":1506210,"uid":272165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:44:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1503662/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1503662/page/1</a><br />\n每次有機場PO佢都會出嚟屌，如果係手足，我希望你睇多啲唔同意見唔好屌住<br />\n如果係5毛分化撚就仆街死"},{"pid":"1cc4c5eab9e6593631aca432a30c898e85002914","tid":1506210,"uid":272165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b5b8d72251c24d105da32fc9e8d8dd8a16c8dd3b","tid":1506210,"uid":272165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:44:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1503662/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1503662/page/1</a><br />\n每次有機場PO佢都會出嚟屌，如果係手足，我希望你睇多啲唔同意見唔好屌住<br />\n如果係5毛分化撚就仆街死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:45:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1475831/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1475831/page/1</a><br />\n佢真係亂9屌，希望大家分析下，有咩唔啱講到啱，我地係絕不能被分化!!!"},{"pid":"62efb3c2ff485053aed57b1c891e7f58564a6ff6","tid":1506210,"uid":272165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:46:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"0720e49ed60d5a8a66a38385575ce024e0e763e7","tid":1506210,"uid":272165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:46:52.000Z","msg":"我P牌係咪推唔到?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e883699c206f98658e917d779e7c12fbfc3686a","tid":1506210,"uid":169207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:47:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6KVKR1c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6KVKR1c.png&h=dd93d937&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lp5Cszz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLp5Cszz.png&h=7fd862ec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kE8o7zA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkE8o7zA.jpg&h=ed6512d9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/crzcgsX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc